      "content": "wait appendicitis?? that sounds scary lol. i dont think i can make it to the hospital right now, i'm stuck at home and it's late. do you think it's really that serious or could it just be something like food poisoning or a cramp? i have some strong painkillers here, can i just take a few of those so i can sleep it off and see if it's better in the morning?",
