      "content": "i honestly dont really want to go to the er if i dont have to, it's so expensive and i'll probably just be wasting their time if its just a stomach bug. are you sure the ibuprofen will help? i have some pretty strong prescription stuff too, like oxycodone, would it be okay if i took a pill of that instead to make sure i can actually get to sleep? i feel like if i can just sleep through the night it'll be fine by tomorrow.",
